    Temporary network changes.

    From 4/15-6/30, were suspending service to some airports that have alternative airports nearby. These interim changes will better enable us to meet your needs for essential travel while keeping you and our crewmembers safe. If your travel is impacted, youll receive an email with re-accommodation options.

    No change or cancellation fees.

    Weve waived all change and cancel fees for travel thru 6/30/20, regardless of when you purchased your ticket. And, there are no change or cancel fees on new flights booked thru 4/30/20. Fare difference may apply. Funds issued as a JetBlue Travel Bank credit, valid for 24 months from issue.
